    </head>
    <body>

        <div class="container">

            <div class="page">
                <h1>Hi There!</h1>
                <h3>My name is Jessica Palay and I've been "learning" how to code.</h3>
            </div>

            <div class="navigation">
                <a id="about" data="about-page">About</a>
                <a id="work" data="work-page">Work</a>
                <a id="contact" data="contact-page">Contact</a>
            </div>

            <div class="navigation-1">
                    <a id="about-1" data-page="about-page">About</a>
                    <a id="work-1" data-page="work-page">Work</a>
                    <a id="contact-1" data-page="contact-page">Contact</a>
            </div>

            <div class="about-page">
                <h1>My story</h1>
                <p>I started learning how to code in June 2013. My curiosity in how new technologies—in particular those related to the internet—impact our lives fueled my desire to experience it firsthard through coding. Now I'm hooked; most of the time you can find me in my "coding cave" googling error messages. Stackoverflow and GitHub gists are my new best friends.</p>
                <p>My skills include Ruby on Rails, jQuery and HTML/CSS.</p>
                <p>I also specialize in digital ethnographic research, digital archaeology and the construction of facts.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="work-page">
              <h1>My sandbox</h1>
              <p>Here are some of the apps I've been working on.</p>
              <div class="container">
                  <div class="project">
                        <a class="project-image" id="img1" href="http://jessicapalaybloccit.herokuapp.com/">
                        </a>
                        <a class="applink" href="http://jessicapalaybloccit.herokuapp.com/">Bloccit</a>
                  </div>
                  <div class="project">
                    <a class="project-image" id="img2" href="http://jessicapalayveggieout.herokuapp.com/">
                    </a>
                    <a class="applink" href="http://jessicapalayveggieout.herokuapp.com/">VeggieOut</a>
                  </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-page">
              <h1>Want to get in touch?</h1>
              <p>Send me an email and I will get back to you.</p>
              <form action="?contact" method="post" class="ajax">
                <fieldset>
                    <input type="text" name="nome" placeholder="NAME" class="required">
                    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="EMAIL" class="required[email]">
                    <textarea name="message" placeholder="MESSAGE" class="required"></textarea>
                    <div class="errormessage"></div>
                    <a class="submit">Send</a>
                </fieldset>
                </form>
            </div>

        </div> <!-- /container -->

    </body>
</html>
